<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Scott Disick has been enjoying some quality time with his three kids, following his split with Sofia Richie.</p>

<p>And the Talentless creator appears to have his hands full with daughter Penelope's most recent playdate. </p>

<p>He was ever the doting dad Tuesday, as he took to his Instagram Story with an adorable photo, while chaperoning a pool party for Penelope, niece North West and some friends.</p>

<p>Pool party: Scott Disick was ever the doting dad Tuesday, as he took to his Instagram Story with an adorable photo, while chaperoning a pool party for Penelope, niece North West and some friends</p>

<p>The 37-year-old posted a snap of the kiddos splashing around in the infinity pool, with a gorgeous scenic view, as he wrote: 'Pool party up in da club.'</p>

<p>He shares Penelope, eight, and sons Mason, 10, and Reign, five, with ex Kourtney Kardashian, 41, with whom he was in an on-again, off-again relationship from 2005 to 2016.  </p>

<p>They recently sparked rumors of another baby on the way, as her sister Kim Kardashian, 39, put them on the spot during a family gathering. </p>

